WEBVTT



00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:04.384
Welcome to the podcast from Perdido Main Methodist Church.

00:00:04.160 --> 00:00:08.064
My name is Dudley. Today is Monday, February 16th.

00:00:08.064 --> 00:00:10.976
We're in Matthew fourteen today.

00:00:10.784 --> 00:00:13.408
This chapter covers a lot of ground.

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:16.736
It begins with the death of John the Baptist.

00:00:16.416 --> 00:00:18.784
Jesus and the disciples.

00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:22.336
Or trying to withdraw to a quiet place.

00:00:22.464 --> 00:00:25.152
And when they attempt to get away,

00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:27.808
The crowds follow Jesus.

00:00:28.352 --> 00:00:32.192
And he has compassion on them even in his sorrow.

00:00:32.224 --> 00:00:37.824
He he has compassion his heart goes out to them and he begins to heal them

00:00:38.080 --> 00:00:42.016
And once he's been with the people and encouraged them and healed them, he's

00:00:42.048 --> 00:00:44.096
The disciples say,

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:47.904
Let's send them away so that they can go somewhere and eat.

00:00:47.648 --> 00:00:49.920
We don't have any food out here.

00:00:49.888 --> 00:00:51.232
But Jesus,

00:00:51.328 --> 00:00:53.536
It tells the disciples,

00:00:53.664 --> 00:00:55.296
You feed the people.

00:00:56.288 --> 00:00:57.504
And you know what?

00:00:57.888 --> 00:01:01.248
Through Jesus's power, they do.

00:01:00.992 --> 00:01:08.256
Feed the people, he multiplies the food. They carry the food around to minister to the people.

00:01:08.288 --> 00:01:11.392
This helps to remember that apart from Jesus,

00:01:11.296 --> 00:01:15.200
Uh, we won't feed anyone, but with him, uh,

00:01:15.008 --> 00:01:19.232
We can see the multitudes fed and encouraged.

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:21.952
Here we see Jesus' compassion.

00:01:22.016 --> 00:01:28.960
Really caring for people, really loving people, and that's the motivation for doing ministry.

00:01:29.216 --> 00:01:36.576
It's not because we have some duty or or we feel obligated, but it's because of love.

00:01:37.216 --> 00:01:40.608
May God continue to develop our compassion.

00:01:40.576 --> 00:01:44.480
And strengthen and anoint us to make a difference.

00:01:45.408 --> 00:01:47.392
Now here's a powerful point.

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:51.232
When Jesus is going to do something through us,

00:01:51.104 --> 00:01:53.920
Lack is not a problem.

00:01:53.664 --> 00:01:55.936
It may look like we don't have enough.

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:59.360
But he is going to bring through.

00:01:59.072 --> 00:02:02.016
The miracle that he is trying to accomplish.

00:02:01.856 --> 00:02:04.832
And he's going to do it through you and through me.

00:02:04.992 --> 00:02:06.688
No matter

00:02:06.592 --> 00:02:12.064
But what? No matter how many, Jesus is able to multiply them.

00:02:12.128 --> 00:02:13.856
That's not a problem.

00:02:13.824 --> 00:02:17.728
He never once said, "I'm worried too."

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:22.752
He just said, Make preparations. I'm going to do something.

00:02:22.912 --> 00:02:23.936
Thank you.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:25.536
When we have nothing,

00:02:25.856 --> 00:02:28.128
We have everything.

00:02:28.096 --> 00:02:29.472
In Jesus.

00:02:30.272 --> 00:02:35.712
The next thing that happens is that Jesus puts the disciples in a boat and then he goes to prayer.

00:02:36.032 --> 00:02:38.176
Later, he comes to them.

00:02:38.336 --> 00:02:42.784
Walking on the water in the middle of a great storm.

00:02:43.328 --> 00:02:47.168
And here I wanted to say that Jesus comes to us.

00:02:46.816 --> 00:02:48.608
In our storms.

00:02:48.704 --> 00:02:53.888
And he comes walking on the very things that we are afraid of.

00:02:54.336 --> 00:02:57.952
And here's something interesting. He enables us.

00:02:58.176 --> 00:03:04.448
to walk on those waves too when our eyes are on him when our faith is in him

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:05.184
We...

00:03:05.376 --> 00:03:06.720
Walk on

00:03:06.464 --> 00:03:09.600
Our fears and our storms.

00:03:09.824 --> 00:03:12.352
Jesus calms the storm and

00:03:12.320 --> 00:03:14.656
And then they reached the other side.

00:03:14.432 --> 00:03:17.696
And Jesus heals people again.

00:03:17.536 --> 00:03:19.936
He goes from making.

00:03:19.744 --> 00:03:21.664
A huge impact.

00:03:21.632 --> 00:03:25.056
To making a huge impact, to making a huge impact.

00:03:24.800 --> 00:03:26.560
And in the middle of that,

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:28.512
He is in prayer.

00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:29.856
And he's

00:03:29.664 --> 00:03:35.104
Walking on the water and he's helping the disciples to do

00:03:34.848 --> 00:03:39.488
The things that he will be doing that makes a difference for others.

00:03:41.472 --> 00:03:44.000
What Jesus is doing in the natural.

00:03:43.904 --> 00:03:47.872
It is simply a picture of what he's doing in the spiritual world.

00:03:47.936 --> 00:03:53.088
Many were healed in the physical, but Jesus is healing people spiritually.

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:55.904
So here's our assignment.

00:03:55.872 --> 00:03:58.336
Simply come to him

00:03:58.368 --> 00:04:00.800
Simply keep our eyes

00:04:00.512 --> 00:04:06.880
On him and learn from him and realize that he is working in and through us.

00:04:07.072 --> 00:04:08.768
2021 in the sunny day.

00:04:08.608 --> 00:04:09.824
Show up.

00:04:09.664 --> 00:04:11.520
100% in times of hunger.

00:04:11.584 --> 00:04:13.792
Show up in times of need.

00:04:13.952 --> 00:04:16.864
We are to show up. We are to be near him.

00:04:16.544 --> 00:04:23.136
And when you're in the storm, realize that Jesus is over that storm and that he is on the way.

00:04:23.264 --> 00:04:24.896
And through his power.

00:04:25.056 --> 00:04:27.904
We will walk on the waves, too.

00:04:28.416 --> 00:04:30.816
Sit with others at Jesus' feet.

00:04:31.104 --> 00:04:34.464
Let your faith be encouraged by Jesus' teaching.

00:04:34.144 --> 00:04:35.584
Follow him.

00:04:35.616 --> 00:04:39.008
Look to him in all the circumstances of your life.

00:04:38.912 --> 00:04:40.352
Worship him

00:04:40.544 --> 00:04:42.816
Ask him for transformation.

00:04:42.944 --> 00:04:45.184
And when he is multiplying

00:04:45.728 --> 00:04:48.320
Jump in and help serve the people.

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:51.808
Realize that what's going on in the natural?

00:04:52.064 --> 00:04:53.792
Is much,

00:04:53.728 --> 00:04:54.816
deeper.

00:04:54.848 --> 00:04:57.088
When we see it in the supernatural.

00:04:57.792 --> 00:04:59.936
We are here for eternity.

00:04:59.776 --> 00:05:02.880
We start in the natural, but we will end up.

00:05:02.944 --> 00:05:04.256
With him.

00:05:04.288 --> 00:05:05.696
in eternity.

00:05:05.568 --> 00:05:08.000
It's like what we read in John 14.

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:09.952
Do not let your hearts be troubled.

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:11.584
You believe in God.

00:05:11.648 --> 00:05:13.408
Believe also in me.

00:05:13.728 --> 00:05:18.016
My father's house has many rooms. If that were not so,

00:05:17.824 --> 00:05:22.592
Would I have told you that I'm going there to prepare a place for you?

00:05:22.880 --> 00:05:25.440
And if I go and prepare a place for you,

00:05:25.344 --> 00:05:28.928
I will come back and take you to be with me.

00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:30.304
That you...

00:05:30.464 --> 00:05:31.648
Also,

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:32.992
Maybe where I am.

00:05:34.432 --> 00:05:35.776
Have a blessed day.
